{"tid":1507873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"OT緊 一停落黎 我淨係諗到一個畫面","createTime":"2019-08-26T10:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:57:23.000Z","uid":27814,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2c673b660e9d810467bc1fe1a517f7b5e15091","tid":1507873,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"好耐無畫過原子筆畫<br />\n對上一次都五六年前 大學讀書果時<br />\n唔經唔覺已經出咗嚟社會五六年<br />\n渾渾噩噩 日日返工等放工<br />\n<br />\n依家OT緊 做嘢做到好攰<br />\n一停落嚟呢埋眼<br />\n我淨係諗到呢個畫面<br />\n<br />\n獻醜 愚人弄技<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHGurch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHGurch.png&h=1fdd1481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信大家依一世都唔會忘記<br />\n<br />\n或許到最後沒有完美句號。"},{"pid":"33ddc2a7940d61623901a89366b40f387089802e","tid":1507873,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=2c084f6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=8759b959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fe2476e6004a34515797cbe8b9b4963b7391e1","tid":1507873,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20